---
// Componente para mostrar los paquetes de certificados
---

<section
  class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 via-white to-blue-50 py-20 lg:py-24"
>
  <!-- Elementos decorativos de fondo -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <div
      class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-300/10 via-blue-200/5 to-transparent rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-gradient-to-tr from-blue-300/8 via-blue-200/5 to-transparent rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse"
      style="animation-delay: 1.5s;"
    >
    </div>

    <!-- Círculos decorativos flotantes -->
    <div
      class="hidden lg:block absolute right-10 top-20 w-4 h-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-blue-400 rounded-full opacity-30 animate-float"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="hidden lg:block absolute left-20 bottom-32 w-5 h-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-300 to-blue-300 rounded-full opacity-20 animate-float"
      style="animation-delay: 1s;"
    >
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Título de la sección -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Paquetes de <span
          class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
          >Certificación</span
        >
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Elige el paquete que mejor se adapte a tus necesidades profesionales y
        obtén el reconocimiento que mereces.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid de paquetes -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
      <!-- Paquete General -->
      <div
        class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl shadow-xl border border-gray-100 p-8 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300"
      >
        <div class="text-center mb-6">
          <div
            class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-4 w-4 mr-2"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            Entrada General
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">PAQUETE GENERAL</h3>
          <div class="text-4xl font-black text-blue-600 mb-4">S/ 10</div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-center text-gray-700">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Asiento reservado</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center text-gray-700">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>            <span>2 tickets para participar en sorteos</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a
          href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeRKLntstbofjfjgkCXhglaxathDv58uOBx3TueVtfXArz_vQ/viewform"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="block w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold py-4 px-6 rounded-xl transition-colors duration-200 text-center"
        >
          Seleccionar Paquete
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Paquete Innova -->
      <div
        class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl shadow-xl border-2 border-blue-200 p-8 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 relative"
      >
        <!-- Badge de recomendado -->
        <div class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
          <div
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-500 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold"
          >
            ⭐ Recomendado
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mb-6 mt-4">
          <div
            class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-4 w-4 mr-2"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            Con Certificado
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">PAQUETE INNOVA</h3>
          <div class="text-4xl font-black text-blue-600 mb-4">S/ 15</div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-center text-gray-700">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Asiento reservado</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center text-gray-700">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>5 tickets para sorteos</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center text-blue-700 font-semibold">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>            <span>Certificado de asistencia oficial</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a
          href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeRKLntstbofjfjgkCXhglaxathDv58uOBx3TueVtfXArz_vQ/viewform"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="block w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold py-4 px-6 rounded-xl transition-colors duration-200 text-center"
        >
          Seleccionar Paquete
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
